<p>Or if you just want to lock onto the angle and not mess with odometry, you can get the tx value from the limelight, then have a drive command that uses your driver input for translation, but uses the tx value for aligning the robot.</p>
<p>This is what our <a href="https://github.com/panthertech292/2024_r/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/commands/Swerve/driveAimAtTarget.java" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">driveAimAtTarget</a> command does.</p>","post_number":2,"post_type":1,"posts_count":7,"updated_at":"2024-03-10T22:01:25.138Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":55,"reads":173,"readers_count":172,"score":329.6,"yours":false,"topic_id":458163,"topic_slug":"swerve-drive-yagsl-w-limelight-autoposition-help","display_username":"Dylan","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":2,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"link_counts":[{"url":"https://github.com/panthertech292/2024_r/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/commands/Swerve/driveAimAtTarget.java","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"2024_r/src/main/java/frc/robot/commands/Swerve/driveAimAtTarget.java at master · panthertech292/2024_r · GitHub","clicks":77},{"url":"https://github.com/LimelightVision/limelightlib-wpijava","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"GitHub - LimelightVision/limelightlib-wpijava","clicks":67},{"url":"https://github.com/panthertech292/2024_r/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/SwerveSubsystem.java","internal":false,"reflection":false,"title":"2024_r/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/SwerveSubsystem.java at master · panthertech292/2024_r · GitHub","clicks":44}],"read":true,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":1}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":51481,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"user_custom_fields":{"user_field_4":""},"post_url":"/t/swerve-drive-yagsl-w-limelight-autoposition-help/458163/2","custom_user_title":null,"react